Class parse.Directories 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----parse.Directories
public class Directories
extends Object
This is a list of all the directories that parser.Parser should look in. It should include all directories containing Parsable objects. It is also used by FindBNF.

This code is (c) 1996,97 Leemon Baird <leemon@cs.cmu.edu>, http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~baird
The source and object code may be redistributed freely. If the code is modified, please state so in the comments.

dirs 
 public static final String dirs[]
A complete list of all packages in WebSim. This list must be complete and accurate in order for WebSim to work correctly.

parsedClasses 
 public static Hashtable parsedClasses
the package names for classes that have been parsed so far

packageHints 
 public static Hashtable packageHints
Some guesses as to the package name for some classes. The program will work correctly, though more slowly, if some classes are missing or have the wrong package name listed, or have a name listed that isn't even an existing package.
